<para id="fs-idm798501568">Keith,<newline/><newline/>



I want to wish you well as you move to the next phase of your life.  I have appreciated in countless ways your supervision, rides home and friendship over the years.  I wish you and your family great success for years to come.<newline/><newline/>
 
All the best,<newline/><newline/>
Bryan</para>

