<note id="fs-idm422337104" class="astronomy making-connections">
<title>January 17, 2019</title>
<para id="fs-idm304652672">(Seeing Keith walk by) BrittanyJ: Man I can’t wait til I retire.</para></note>

<para id="fs-idm273177760">
Retirement is the end of one chapter and the beginning of a new one. Let’s hope the next chapter of Keith’s life is as good or better as his previous. Congratulations! - Ivy</para>

<note id="fs-idm352307008" class="astronomy voyagers-in-astronomy">
<title>Debshila's driving</title>
<para id="fs-idm371042848">The only thing I have to say is that he doesn’t trust my driving, and I am not sure why. - Debshila</para>
</note>

 <figure id="fs-idm869313472"><media id="fs-idm868573712" alt="Alt test for Art Asset">
